  "content": {
    "prompt": "<div><div class=\"stimulus_reference\"><div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows a rectangular circuit with a battery, three lightbulbs, and a switch. The left vertical branch has the battery. The middle vertical branch has Bulb 2. The right vertical branch has the switch, which is open. The top horizontal branch has, between the middle and right vertical branched, Bulb 1. The bottom horizontal branch has, between the middle and right vertical branches, Bulb 3.\" src=\"/images/786bcfd243e0c5f4fe234118bd160cdf.svg\"></div></div></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">A circuit is created using an ideal battery, three lightbulbs, and a switch, as shown in the figure. The switch is initially open and is then closed. What happens to the brightness of bulbs <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1\"><math alttext=\"1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>1</mn></math></span></span> and <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2\"><math alttext=\"2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn></math></span></span> when the switch is closed?</p><div class=\"table_wrapper\"><table class=\"tgroup align:center cols:3 colsep:0 frame:none rowsep:0\"><colgroup><col class=\"colspec colname:col1 colnum:1 colsep:1\"></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\"><tr class=\"row rowsep:1\"><th class=\"entry colname:col1\"></th><th class=\"entry colname:col2\">Bulb <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1\"><math alttext=\"1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>1</mn></math></span></span></th><th class=\"entry colname:col3\">Bulb <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2\"><math alttext=\"2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn></math></span></span></th></tr></thead><tbody class=\"tbody\"><tr class=\"row\"><td class=\"entry colname:col1\">A</td><td class=\"entry colname:col2\">Becomes brighter</td><td class=\"entry colname:col3\">Becomes dimmer</td></tr><tr class=\"row\"><td class=\"entry colname:col1\">B</td><td class=\"entry colname:col2\">Becomes brighter</td><td class=\"entry colname:col3\">Remains the same</td></tr><tr class=\"row\"><td class=\"entry colname:col1\">C</td><td class=\"entry colname:col2\">Remains the same</td><td class=\"entry colname:col3\">Becomes dimmer</td></tr><tr class=\"row\"><td class=\"entry colname:col1\">D</td><td class=\"entry colname:col2\">Remains the same</td><td class=\"entry colname:col3\">Remains the same</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n",
